      "audioDurationSec": 8.907755,
      "textHash": "2070cfb258dc6be53e30313208666ccbdaac862e1dcfff7ece94122f9f5072a0",
      "narrationText": "ألقِ نظرة داخل repo واعرض ما وصل: ملف Rediaccfile يحتوي على hooks التشغيل والإيقاف، وملف docker-compose يصف containers.",
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-deploy-app/tutorial-deploy-app-03-after.e6b5d919.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 6.347755,
      "afterTextHash": "e6b5d91909508ef9f51ef81c94e32547c9e9073a3d19915a85990e92eadeee30"
    },
